flowchart TB
  START([User opens feature area]) --> VIEW{Primary view}
  VIEW -->|View A| WORKSPACE[Main workspace]
  VIEW -->|View B| WORKSPACE

  WORKSPACE --> ACT{Action}
  ACT -->|Open item| DETAIL[Detail view]
  ACT -->|Change state| VALID{Allowed?}
  VALID -->|No| BLOCK[Blocked or feedback]
  VALID -->|Yes| MODAL{Needs confirmation?}
  MODAL -->|Destructive or complex| CONFIRM[Confirmation dialog]
  MODAL -->|Simple update| API[Persist change]
  CONFIRM --> API
  MODAL -->|Missing prerequisite| PROMPT[Prompt or guided flow]
  PROMPT -->|Continue| API
  PROMPT -->|Cancel| WORKSPACE

  DETAIL --> RELATED[Related context]
  RELATED --> WORKSPACE
  API --> WORKSPACE

  style START fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b
  style DETAIL fill:#eef2ff,stroke:#4f46e5
  style API fill:#ecfdf5,stroke:#059669
